==English==

===Noun phrase===
'''[[hyperbolic]] [[tangent]]'''

#{{mathematics}} a [[hyperbolic function]] that is written in symbol [[tanh]] and defined as the following:
:<math>\tanh(x) = \frac{sinh(x)}{cosh(x)} = \frac{e^x - e^{-x}}{e^x + e^{-x}}</math>

===See also===
*[[hyperbolic sine]]
*[[hyperbolic cosine]]

